<div style="display: none;">
  <h3>{{t "Disability-Specific" key='disability_vocabulary'}}</h3>
  <p>{{t "Every person is different, but some disabilities cause similar enough characteristics that creating boards tailored to a specific group of people makes sense. It's important to note that just because a board is labelled for a certain disability doesn't mean it will or won't work well for an individual with that diability -- but it may be a good starting point. Below are a list of disability-specific home boards:" key='disability_vocabulary1'}}</p>
  <div id="disability_vocabulary">
